{"tid":2398852,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析] 話你知點解周杰倫音樂水平高過椎名林檎一個層次","createTime":"2021-02-07T15:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T01:08:40.000Z","uid":353419,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd71defc6d27f0e6ab01a4b80d71d8933144f99a","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=14G_t5Z6k-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D14G_t5Z6k-s&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=d8a248fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=14G_t5Z6k-s</a><br />\n<br />\n椎名林檎呢首浴室, 單係相同的副歌, 總共有4--5次不同效果,<br />\n佢的chord progression不按常理出牌,從而造此好獨特既旋律同氣氛<br />\n樂器的鋪排好豐富, 而且仲加上左好多樂器既聲效,<br />\n用左大量複雜進階的技巧, 變幻莫測, 而將佢地融會貫通.<br />\n歌曲後段營造出一種自殺慘叫的聲音, 同主音配服得好好.<br />\n可見編曲既精密,嚴格,同埋繁華.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ur-x4pZT1Rk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUr-x4pZT1Rk&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=f325541e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ur-x4pZT1Rk</a><br />\n<br />\n然後聽周杰倫的外婆, <br />\n明明佢用的Chord好大路,旋律手法好簡單,編曲亦都比較粗糙,<br />\n基本上佢的構造同一般公廁流行曲冇分別,<br />\n但係...感覺同其他大路歌好似, 但又不盡相同,<br />\n中段小朋友聲同周杰倫對唱, 將氣氛推到極致,<br />\n明明只係不斷重覆既背景音樂, 但好有氣派! <br />\n即使旋律手法好大路, 但周杰倫寫得一啲都唔大路<br />\n我地聽開日本歌,以為編曲技巧一定豐富高階先勁,<br />\n但周杰倫反逆道其行,即使好簡單好粗糙,原來都可以震撼世人!<br />\n實在...實在太好聽啦!!!<br />\n<br />\n令我聯想到...<br />\n椎名林檎就好似唐牛咁,用大量上等材料融合埋一齊,整左個無敵佛跳牆,照咁睇無得輸.<br />\n但周杰倫好似食神咁,用最Cheap隨處可見的叉燒,蛋, 好簡單煮熟佢, 但係....好食到飛起!<br />\n<br />\n又令我聯想到...椎名林檎好似金輪法王咁, 將五個高難度既金輪都舞得掂, 招式層出不窮! 而周杰倫就好似獨孤救敗咁, 拎住條樹枝, 用最簡單的招式,一下秒撚左金輪法王.<br />\n<br />\n反樸歸真, 平凡中見不平凡, 草木皆為劍, <br />\n所以點解...周杰倫的境界高於椎名林檎<br />\n歌舞伎町既女王,又點會嬴到十一月的蕭邦?<br />\n就好似四皇同海賊王的級別之差."},{"pid":"efe4cbebc22ade61819a49049e73eeee48c93bf5","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"3c75b892c5649dea4874a7342dbc258d9f767c99","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:48:25.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"7a10320467c1e94860638fd0f2e9aa5c29308ebc","tid":2398852,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"lm睇世界大戰"},{"pid":"3a5c5ecf2c6e35d8a3c1cceb2797a7e292fded9d","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaM7qG2ycjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaaM7qG2ycjk&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=6ebfaf97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaM7qG2ycjk</a><br />\n<br />\n用文言文黎Rap"},{"pid":"d30f03e359a40ff0e5cde5294c899dfc298f77c1","tid":2398852,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"咪又係輸比加拿大電鏝"},{"pid":"8bcc98d0f548b1148e55d09ef4cf9f05b69f05b9","tid":2398852,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"講咩都無謂<br />\n<br />\n檎迷同倫迷各拎5首歌head to head出黎隻抽"},{"pid":"898826e7c787e38a881fb8fc36d7444a0f0af2fe","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30f03e359a40ff0e5cde5294c899dfc298f77c1","tid":2398852,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"咪又係輸比加拿大電鏝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"周杰倫VS 椎名林檎<br />\n呢個戰場無你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,"},{"pid":"a279016f600c63e399e42aee17ef6027a284624c","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:53:59.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"afabcd838a431238e06ac502ba5d3c471d65bb96","tid":2398852,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"."},{